reviewText: I had a lot of work to do this course and all that are in English. I copy everything in English, put it on Google Traducts and print it to be able to understand it in my language. Some have subtitles but this one doesn't. What made it very difficult but I persisted, I understood and concluded. Thanks for the opportunity. I use canva so these tools will be very useful for me
It is good and use ful for all student. Rajani kumari
